    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>Protocol describing the public surface of an audio manager used by the engine.

This mirrors the primary methods provided by `MusicAndAmbienceManager` so
other engine components can accept a typed audio manager without depending
on the concrete implementation.
</verbatim> </para>
